  <summary>2/27/2001--Introduced.
Medical Research Investment Act of 2001 - Amends the Internal Revenue Code to provide a special limitation for charitable contributions for medical research. Permits the carryover (for 10 succeeding years) of any excess of such contribution.Provides for the special treatment of medical research incentive stock options.</summary>
